486
01:03:32,061 --> 01:03:33,971
Yo no soy Elisabet.

487
01:03:34,356 --> 01:03:37,067
No vengo a exigirte nada.

488
01:03:37,077 --> 01:03:39,190
No quería molestarte.

489
01:03:39,528 --> 01:03:41,354
¿No crees que lo entiendo?

490
01:03:41,780 --> 01:03:44,069
